{"tid":1617161,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"踩隻腳落人哋對鞋","createTime":"2019-10-03T16:19:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T18:19:47.000Z","uid":327205,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b09339245074e206c2473a91e27a049cb43e1934","tid":1617161,"uid":327205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T16:19:42.000Z","msg":"環保分子 Extinction Rebellion，在英國倫敦財政部大樓對出，用假血示威，造成血濺城市畫面，睇落都幾恐怖。<br />\n<br />\nClimate activists spray UK finance ministry with fake blood<br />\n<a href=\"https://edition.cnn.com/2019/10/03/uk/uk-finance-ministry-extinction-rebellion-gbr-intl-scli/index.html?utm_term=link&amp;utm_content=2019-10-03T12%3A20%3A09&amp;utm_source=twCNNi&amp;utm_medium=social\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2019%2F10%2F03%2Fuk%2Fuk-finance-ministry-extinction-rebellion-gbr-intl-scli%2Findex.html%3Futm_term%3Dlink%26utm_content%3D2019-10-03T12%253A20%253A09%26utm_source%3DtwCNNi%26utm_medium%3Dsocial&d=beIwg85N8Ddzcl6rIyS0GQPtErjweJPees2C482IDEo%3D&h=97e8a7f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2019%2F10%2F03%2Fuk%2Fuk-finance-ministry-extinction-rebellion-gbr-intl-scli%2Findex.html%3Futm_term%3Dlink%26utm_content%3D2019-10-03T12%253A20%253A09%26utm_source%3DtwCNNi%26utm_medium%3Dsocial&h=336c8065\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://edition.cnn.com/2019/10/03/uk/uk-finance-ministry-extinction-rebellion-gbr-intl-scli/index.html?utm_term=link&amp;utm_content=2019-10-03T12%3A20%3A09&amp;utm_source=twCNNi&amp;utm_medium=social</a><br />\n<br />\n緊貼環保份子示威的人，完全支持佢哋，因為明白政府無視環保份子訴求，佢哋唯有把行動升級。<br />\n<br />\n畫面經社交媒體傳遍整個世界，好多人唔係中堅份子，唔會日日追住佢哋嘅新聞，一見到呢個畫面好反感。覺得驚又有，覺得影響市容又有，另外有人笑佢哋爭取環保，而家咁做就係浪費等等。<br />\n<br />\n我想講嘅係，世界上絕大部分人都係支持香港爭取民主自由，明白中共獨裁及血腥鎮壓嘅恐怖，睇下929有好多地方參加就知道。<br />\n<br />\n但佢哋唔會每分每秒緊貼我哋情況，尤其佢哋唔識中文，見到我哋不斷破壞，完全明白係政府逼出嚟，但始終都會皺眉頭。<br />\n<br />\n我不是割蓆，亦不是反對還擊，只係想睇下點樣令到呢個世界明白我哋的訴求。例如，會唔會玩水浸，或者好似今晚太古，迫到狗出嚟，令到MTR shops 收鋪無生意，跟住就走等等。<br />\n<br />\nPut yourself in others' shoes"},{"pid":"9225e57f7b911368f71546226422d0711cca41d8","tid":1617161,"uid":327205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T16:21:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kcSGcae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkcSGcae.jpg&h=7837b657&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"05df70e0be8b49c7c5805540db91c6b59f6318af","tid":1617161,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T17:16:39.000Z","msg":"果架係消防車?? 環保人士點拎到??"},{"pid":"158b77c3907239ca1060affac2a871b8aaef51b4","tid":1617161,"uid":327205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05df70e0be8b49c7c5805540db91c6b59f6318af","tid":1617161,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T17:16:39.000Z","msg":"果架係消防車?? 環保人士點拎到??"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T18:19:47.000Z","msg":"問得好， 我都有呢個疑問 ，但真係唔知。因為我都冇緊貼佢哋。<br />\n呢個亦顯示 ，唔熟識當地文化，即係外國人睇香港，真係唔知來龍去脈"}]}